### 1. Register (or skip if already registered)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.demo@tutorhub.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "displayName": "Maria"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("mariaToken", response.body.token);
%}

### 2. Register a student — IMPORTANT: use a real email you can check in Mailtrap
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "chaitanyagelivi03@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "displayName": "Sara"
}

### 3. Create an academy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/academies
Authorization: Bearer {{mariaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo Academy",
  "slug": "demo-academy"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("academyId", response.body.id);
%}

### 4. Add Sara as a STUDENT in the academy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members
Authorization: Bearer {{mariaToken}}
X-Academy-Id: {{academyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "chaitanyagelivi03@gmail.com",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 5. Create a course
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{mariaToken}}
X-Academy-Id: {{academyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Algebra I",
  "subject": "Math",
  "term": "Fall 2026"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("courseId", response.body.id);
%}

### 6. Enroll Sara in the course
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/{{courseId}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{mariaToken}}
X-Academy-Id: {{academyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentEmail": "chaitanyagelivi03@gmail.com"
}

### 7. Create an assignment due in ~2 hours (within the 24h window)
###    IMPORTANT: replace dueDate with a real timestamp 2 hours from NOW (UTC, ISO-8601).
###    Example below assumes current UTC time is roughly 2026-06-17T22:00:00Z.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/{{courseId}}/assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{mariaToken}}
X-Academy-Id: {{academyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Homework 1",
  "instructions": "Complete chapter 1 exercises",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-18T04:37:52Z",
  "maxScore": 100
}
